result.name: Lu Xianzi Taiwanese Restaurant

reviews.text: Average Taiwanese food but very busy during lunch time.
nice

I went during 下午茶 but their special 下午茶 menu is crazy and barely has any Taiwanese items at all on it, and is instead mostly Cantonese mainstays.

I instead got the 滷水雞牌飯 with 珍珠奶茶. It was pretty good, a quick fix for any Taiwanese cravings.
唔算貴，但同樣價錢有更多更好選擇
好好味的肉燥飯，不過我更愛他的雞肶飯
